<br>
My answer is because it's too damn boring and time-consuming and I would rather just take my 1HS and 2HS skills and have fun playing the game until i quit.<br>
<br>
Sure 2HS and 2HB make it possible to hit for amazing amounts of damage, but I find that unless I want to show off, I switch to a pair of good, low-delay 1HS weapons. No matter what Verant says, dual wield still has way more taunt factor than any 2H skill.<br>
<br>
I used to play an enchanter and I now value my ability to save the life of enchanters rather than hit for big numbers.<br>
